# {{.Name}} ({{.Type}})

{{ .Description | trimspace }}

Anomaly detection identifies unusual patterns in data based on historical data patterns. ML jobs search for anomalies in continuous data streams or in batch data. You can create ML anomaly detection jobs for many types of data.

See the [Elasticsearch ML anomaly detection documentation](https://www.elastic.co/guide/en/elasticsearch/reference/current/ml-ad-apis.html).

